tion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Pentagon%20and%20State%20Department%20have%20now%20stepped%20up%20private%20appeals%20for%20caution%20in%20conversations%20with%20the%20Israelis%2C%20two%20sources%20familiar%20with%20discussions%20said%2C%20as%20Israel's%20blockade%20of%20Gaza%20worsens%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis%20and%20the%20death%20toll%20from%20its%20bombardment%20of%20the%20enclave%20passes%205%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20U.S.%20priority%20is%20to%20allow%20more%20time%20for%20negotiations%20on%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20unexpected%20release%20of%20two%20Americans%20on%20Friday.%20Hamas%20said%20it%20released%20two%20more%20hostages%20on%20Monday.%20Hamas%20is%20believed%20to%20hold%20more%20than%20200%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20U.S.%20official%20said%20the%20administration%2C%20mindful%20of%20Doha's%20role%20as%20an%20intermediary%20with%20Hamas%2C%20was%20keeping%20Qatari%20officials%20informed%20of%20its%20advice%20to%20Israel%20so%20that%20they%20are%20fully%20up-to-speed%20as%20hostage%20negotiations%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20there's%20no%20clear%20roadmap%20or%20sequence%20of%20the%20steps%20towards%20complete%20de-escalation.%20The%20priority%20is%20on%20working%20to%20get%20the%20hostages%20out%20step-by-step%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source%20briefed%20on%20the%20hostage%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E'Tough%20Questions'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20second%20U.S.%20official%20said%20that%20European%20governments%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20also%20have%20citizens%20being%20held%20hostage%2C%20were%20also%20suggesting%20Israel%20refrain%20from%20launching%20its%20ground%20offensive%20to%20give%20space%20for%20the%20negotiations%20on%20their%20release%20to%20play%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20discussed%20the%20hostage%20and%20humanitarian%20crises%20in%20Gaza%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20Canada%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%20and%20Britain%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20U.S.%20official%20said%20that%20along%20with%20the%20hostage%20negotiations%2C%20advising%20Israel%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20its%20invasion%20could%20also%20give%20more%20time%20for%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20be%20delivered%20to%20Gaza.%20Since%20Saturday%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20said%2054%20trucks%20of%20aid%20had%20been%20able%20to%20enter%20Gaza%20from%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20national%20security%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20conflict%20Washington%20had%20been%20speaking%20with%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bascertain%20their%20intentions%2C%20their%20strategy%2C%20their%20aims%2C%20to%20see%20what%20their%20answers%20are%2C%20to%20the%20kinds%20of%20tough%20questions%20that%20any%20military%20ought%20to%20be%20asking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20U.S.%20defense%20official%20said%20that%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20-%20in%20many%20phone%20calls%20with%20his%20Israeli%20counterpart%20-%20had%20emphasized%20the%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20knock-on%20effects%20of%20a%20ground%20offensive%2C%20which%20include%20the%20risks%20of%20widening%20conflict%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20hostages%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EU.S.%20officials%20have%20urged%20Israel%20to%20follow%20the%20laws%20of%20war%20in%20any%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%202.3%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20Defense%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20have%20increasingly%20signaled%20in%20public%20that%20a%20Gaza%20invasion%20could%20be%20imminent.%20None%20has%20given%20a%20hard%20date%2C%20however%2C%20or%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20deferment.%20Israel%20has%20called%20up%20a%20record%20300%2C000%20military%20reservists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%2C%20when%20we%20need%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Israel's%20Deputy%20Ambassador%20to%20Washington%20Eliav%20Benjamin%20on%20told%20Israel's%20Army%20Radio%20Monday%2C%20playing%20down%20U.S.%20sway%20on%20planning%20for%20an%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Sunday%2C%20Israel%20has%20signaled%20a%20shift%20in%20tactics%20by%20sending%20infantry%2C%20backed%20by%20tanks%2C%20on%20probing%20incursions%20of%20Gaza%20that%20have%20touched%20off%20clashes%20with%20Hamas%20fighters.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20focusing%20air%20strikes%20on%20what%20it%20described%20as%20areas%20where%20Hamas%20is%20assembling%20its%20fighters%20to%20ambush%20any%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvising%20Israel%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20a%20ground%20offensive%20also%20allows%20Washington%20to%20prepare%20for%20any%20possible%20retaliatory%20attacks%20against%20U.S.%20interests%20in%20the%20region%20as%20fears%20of%20a%20spillover%20grow%2C%20particularly%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon's%20heavily-armed%2C%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20that%20there's%20a%20likelihood%20of%20escalation%20...%20We%20are%20taking%20steps%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20can%20effectively%20defend%20our%20people%20and%20respond%20decisively%20if%20we%20need%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20U.S.%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20told%20NBC%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20also%20grown%20concerned%20over%20the%20desire%20among%20some%20senior%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%2C%20advocating%20for%20a%20pre-emptive%20strike%20on%20Hezbollah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20would%20have%20a%20difficult%20time%20fighting%20a%20war%20on%20two%20fronts%20simultaneously%20i