ks-reports-2023-10%5C%22%3EOctober%207%2C%202023%2C%20incursion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth-grader%20from%20the%20central%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Kfar%20Saba%20was%20nabbed%20along%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20grandparents%20during%20a%20holiday%20visit%20to%20his%20grandparents'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwar-correspondent-says-horror-israel-kibbutz-reminds-him-of-isis-2023-10%5C%22%3Ekibbutz%20of%20Nir%20Oz%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhad's%20beloved%20uncle%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20The%20boy%2C%20his%20mom%2C%20and%20his%20grandparents%20disappeared%20with%20the%20only%20thread%20of%20information%20about%20them%20coming%20from%20a%20cellphone%20signal%20traced%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20that%20uncertainty%20that%20has%20been%20most%20agonizing%20for%20Ohad's%20grief-stricken%20father%2C%20Avi%20Zichri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20keep%20imagining%20what%20he%20is%20going%20through.%20He's%20a%20sensitive%20boy.%20Did%20he%20see%20dead%20bodies%3F%20He%20wears%20glasses.%20Did%20they%20take%20them%20from%20him%3F%20Can%20he%20see%20anything%3F%26quot%3B%20Zichri%20said%20as%20he%20nervously%20chain-smoked%20cigarettes%20on%20his%20front%20porch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20keep%20thinking%20of%20every%20scenario%2C%20hoping%20for%20the%20least%20catastrophic.%20I%20just%20hope%20that%20he%20is%20safe%20and%20with%20his%20mother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZichri%20has%20been%20living%20this%20nightmare%20for%2017%20days%2C%20saying%20the%20thoughts%20never%20leave%20him%20and%20the%20only%20reprieve%20comes%20when%20he%20takes%20sleeping%20pills%20that%20knock%20him%20out%20for%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20feel%20guilty%20for%20not%20thinking%20about%20them%20in%20my%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2069-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhad%20is%20Zichri's%20only%20child%20with%20his%20partner%2C%20Keren%20Munder%2C%20a%2054-year-old%20special%20education%20teacher%20and%20volleyball%20coach%20for%20children%20with%20disabilities.%20He's%20also%20the%20only%20grandson%20of%20Avraham%20and%20Ruti%20Munder%2C%20both%2078%2C%20who%20disappeared%20with%20them%20from%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20where%20about%2080%20people%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20residents%20of%20the%20small%20community%20%E2%80%94%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20taken%20hostage.%20Ohad%20loved%20visiting%20his%20grandparents%20and%20his%20uncle%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20he%20is%20a%20gifted%20student%20who%20loves%20solving%20Rubik's%20cubes%20and%20playing%20soccer%2C%20tennis%2C%20and%20chess.%20He%20is%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20Liverpool%20FC%20and%20his%20bedroom%2C%20untouched%20since%20his%20abduction%2C%20includes%20team%20souvenirs%2C%20his%20various%20trophies%2C%20family%20photos%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20and%20the%20elaborate%20Lego%20constructions%20he%20loved%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20incredibly%20smart%20and%20charming%20and%20is%20very%20developed%20verbally.%20He%20teaches%20me%20things%20all%20the%20time%20and%20I%20sometimes%20forget%20that%20he%20is%20only%209%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Zichri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonday's%20birthday%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20Ohad's%20plight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20outpouring%20of%20local%20and%20international%20support.%20The%20Israeli%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Michael%20Herzog%2C%20launched%20an%20international%20social%20media%20campaign%2C%20calling%20on%20people%20to%20send%20him%20virtual%20birthday%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20Ohad's%20favorite%20Israeli%20soccer%20team%20and%20other%20prominent%20Israeli%20athletes%20have%20recorded%20birthday%20greetings%20and%20wishes%20for%20his%20safe%20return.%20Yellow%20balloons%20with%20messages%20recognizing%20his%20birthday%20in%20captivity%20were%20strewn%20across%20his%20hometown%20of%20Kfar%20Saba%2C%20with%20other%20local%20initiatives%20taking%20place.%20Local%20media%20widely%20acknowledged%20the%20day%20and%20friends%20posted%20tributes%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhad's%20family%20members%20spoke%20with%20CNN%20about%20the%209-year-old%20and%20were%20asked%20what%20they'd%20say%20to%20those%20who%20apparently%20have%20him%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2023%2F10%2F23%2Fmerav-raviv-itay-raviv-jake-tapper-live.cnn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItay%20Raviv%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20innocent.%20They%20are%20innocent%20civilians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20especially%20called%20for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20children.%20At%20least%2020%20of%20the%20hostages%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20children%20and%20teens%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-war-hostages-family-missing-boy-birthday-rcna121284%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces'%20estimates%20last%20week.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ask%20all%20media%20for%20everyone%20in%20Israel%20to%20hang%20a%20balloon%2C%26quot%3B%20Merav%20Raviv%2C%20the%20niece%20of%20Avraham%20and%20Ruti%20Munder%2C%20told%20CNN's%20Jake%20Tapper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Zichri%2C%20Ohad's%20father%2C%20it%20was%20just%20another%20in%20a%20series%20of%20agonizing%20days%2C%20with%20anxiety%20consuming%20his%20every%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20could%20celebrate%20with%20him%20today.%20But%20it%20feels%20no%20different.%20It's%20just%20wake%20up%20and%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20every%20day%20it%20gets%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZichri%20was%20awaiting%20Ohad%20and%20his%20mom's%20return%20on%20October%207%20when%20he%20heard%20air-raid%20sirens%20warning%20of%20incoming%20rockets.%20He%20instinctively%20reached%20out%20to%20Munder%20knowing%20that%20she%20and%20Ohad%20were%20in%20much%20closer%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPulling%20out%20his%20cellphone%2C%20Zichri%20showed%20their%20final%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nonstop%20firing%20here%20and%20there%20is%20concern%20terrorists%20have%20infiltrated%20the%20villages%2C%26quot%3B%20Munder%20wrote%20at%207%3A24%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20that%20they%20were%20hiding%20in%20the%20safe%20room%20and%20she%20had%20locked%20the%20door.%20She%20said%20she%20forgot%20her%20cellphone%20charger%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20might%20soon%20run%20out%20of%20battery%2C%20but%20she%20managed%20to%20let%20Zichri%20know%20they%20had%20turned%20off%20the%20news%20so%20that%20Ohad%20could%20quietly%20watch%20a%20TV%20show%20to%20distract%20him%20from%20what%20was%20going%20on%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20hope%20this%20ends%20quickly%20with%20no%20one%20getting%20harmed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20last%20message%20at%207%3A39%20a.m.%20%26quot%3BTake%20care%20of%20yourself%20and%20follow%20the%20homefront%20command%20instructions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZichri%20said%20it%20was%20typical%20of%20Munder%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20worry%20about%20others%20before%20herself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZichri%20said%20he%20shudders%20at%20every%20report%20of%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20in%20Gaza%2C%20wondering%20if%20they%20had%20harmed%20his%20loved%20ones.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20keeps%20him%20going%20throughout%20the%20endless%2C%20agonizing%20wait%20for%20information%20is%20the%20support%20of%20a%20small%20group%20of%20friends%20and%20a%20vision%20of%20one%20day%20reuniting%20with%20his%20son%20and%20Munder%2C%20and%20falling%20into%20their%20arms%20in%20a%20tearful%20embrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20do%20is%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%2