%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Famazon-let-its-drivers-urine-be-sold-as-an-energy-drink%2F%23intcid%3D_wired-verso-hp-trending_f565265d-9362-4113-a045-d03f49f80bc8_popular4-1%5C%22%3Etold%20WIRED%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bsurprisingly%20easy%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20the%20product%20listed%20on%20the%20site%20and%20Amazon's%20algorithm%20moved%20the%20product%20into%20its%20drinks%20category%20on%20the%20site%20after%20he'd%20put%20it%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BRefillable%20Pump%20Dispenser%26quot%3B%20category.%20While%20Butler%20got%20some%20friends%20to%20purchase%20the%20product%20and%20never%20sold%20the%20item%20to%20any%20real%20customers%2C%20he%20told%20Insider%20he%20estimated%20that%20he%20had%20about%2010%20genuine%20customers%20who%20tried%20to%20buy%20the%20product%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERelease%20has%20since%20been%20taken%20off%20the%20Amazon%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221325%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Release%20was%20listed%20on%20Amazon%2C%20but%20has%20since%20been%20taken%20down.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536c4dd96f7540cd06344c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERelease%20was%20listed%20on%20Amazon%2C%20but%20has%20since%20been%20taken%20down.%3Cp%3EWayBack%20Machine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Release%20Energy's%20story%20lies%20a%20dedication%20to%20empowering%20Amazon%20delivery%20drivers%2C%20unsung%20heroes%20who%20face%20immense%20pressures%20navigating%20impossibly%20demanding%20schedules%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20portion%20of%20Release's%20production%20description%20reads.%20%26quot%3BTasked%20with%20impossibly%20tight%20deadlines%2C%20these%20drivers%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20relentless%20race%20against%20time%2C%20often%20sacrificing%20their%20own%20needs%20to%20ensure%20packages%20reach%20their%20destinations.%20Release%20Energy%20was%20born%20from%20the%20desperation%