%20his%20upper%20left%20arm%3B%20blistering%3B%20peeling%2C%20bleeding%3B%20possible%20permanent%20cosmetic%20deformity%20and%20scarring%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20New%20York%20and%20obtained%20by%20Insider%2C%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatorre%20claims%20that%20even%20the%20tattoo%20on%20his%20arm%20was%20left%20badly%20damaged%20by%20the%20cup%20of%20joe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20complaint%20Monday%2C%20an%20American%20Airlines%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20that%20it%20cannot%20comment%20on%20pending%20legal%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20says%20that%20the%20cup%20of%20java%20wound%20up%20on%20Latorre%20as%20he%20was%20sitting%20in%20seat%2033J.%20American%20Airlines%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bcareless%2C%20reckless%2C%20and%20negligent%20in%20serving%20scalding%20coffee%20to%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20an%20unsafe%20manner%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20hire%20and%20retain%20competent%20personnel%20and%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatorre%20has%20undergone%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20pain%20and%20suffering%3B%20emotional%20harm%2C%20mental%20anguish%20and%20distress%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20sleep%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20pain%20and%20will%20require%20medical%20care%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says%20the%20airline%20refused%20to%20let%20Latorre%20purchase%20a%20business%20class%20seat%20with%20extra%20legroom%20after%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bburned%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20coffee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatorre%20sought%20medical%20attention%20after%20the%20flight%20landed%20and%20was%20told%20that%20his%20injuries%20were%20%26quot%3Bserious%20enough%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20had%20to%20see%20a%20surgeon%2C%20Jaroslawicz%2C%20Latorre's%20attorney%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3