%20photography%20reveals%20the%20symbols%20of%20a%20Christogram%20and%20the%20Alpha%20and%20Omega%20Greek%20letters.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologists%20studying%20a%20burial%20site%20near%20a%20medieval%20monastery%20spotted%20a%20rare%20find%20when%20examining%20one%20of%20the%20bodies%3A%20the%20faint%20remains%20of%20a%20series%20of%20Christian%20symbols%20tattooed%20on%20the%20person's%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20quite%20a%20surprise%20to%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20see%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20tattoo%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kari%20A.%20Guilbault%2C%20a%20Purdue%20University%20bioarchaeologist%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Warsaw.%20%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20not%20certain%2C%20but%20when%20the%20images%20were%20processed%20and%20the%20tattoo%20was%20clearly%20visible%2C%20any%20initial%20uncertainties%20were%20removed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tattoo%20%E2%80%94%20located%20on%20the%20top%20of%20one%20of%20the%20bodies'%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20is%20of%20the%20Greek%20letters%20Alpha%20and%20Omega%20as%20well%20as%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3BChristogram%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20religious%20symbol%20combining%20the%20Greek%20letters%20Chi%20and%20Rho%20to%20make%20an%20abbreviation%20for%20Christ's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20released%20images%20of%20the%20tattoo%20taken%20with%20a%20full-spectrum%20camera%20and%20digitally%20enhanced%20to%20show%20the%20outline%20of%20the%20early%20Christian%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20investigating%20the%20Ghazali%20monastery%2C%20a%20well-preserved%20archeological%20site%20located%20in%20Sudan%2C%20according%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Warsaw's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20in%20the%20Bayuda%20desert%20was%20initially%20studied%20between%202012%20and%202018%20when%20a%20Polish-Sudanese%20team%20explored%20the%20monastery%20and%20the%20surrounding%20four%20burial%20sites%20and%20their%20hundreds%20of%20graves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20took%20photos%20of%20some%20buried%20bodies%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20people%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20area.%20While%20reviewing%20the%20photos%2C%20Guilbault%20spotted%20the%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuilbault%20and%20bioarchaeologist%20Robert%20Stark%20of%20the%20Polish%20Centre%20of%20Mediterranean%20Archaeology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Warsaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Farchaeology%2Fchrist-tattoo-discovered-on-1300-year-old-body-in-sudan%5C%22%3Etold%20LiveScience%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20location%20of%20the%20tattoo%20was%20intriguing%20since%20it%20may%20line%20up%20with%20where%20Jesus%20is%20said%20to%20have%20had%20a%20nail%20driven%20through%20during%20his%20crucifixion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20wasn't%20buried%20in%20the%20same%20cemetery%20as%20the%20monastery's%20monks%20but%20rather%20in%20a%20burial%20ground%20that%20may%20have%20been%20used%20by%20people%20from%20nearby%20communities%2C%20Stark%20and%20Guilbault%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20told%20LiveScience%20that%20the%20person%20lived%20sometime%20between%20667%20and%20774%20and%20was%20buried%20in%20a%20burial%20ground%20that%20may%20have%20been%20used%20by%20members%20of%20the%20nearby%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristian-symbols-found-tattooed-on-medieval-bodys-foot-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698089474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536b9fa0487ff031cabf1e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristian-symbols-found-tattooed-on-medieval-bodys-foot-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rare%20tattoo%20was%20found%20on%20the%20foot%20of%20a%20person%20buried%20near%20a%20medieval%20monastery%20in%20Sudan%2C%20archeologists%20announced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psquire%40insider.