EY's%20chief%20economist%20estimated.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20stock%20market's%20fear%20gauge%20could%20spike%2018%20points%20as%20volatility%20soars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20could%20surge%20well%20into%20to%20the%20triple-digits%20and%20market%20volatility%20could%20skyrocket%20in%20the%20most%20severe%20scenario%20of%20an%20uncontained%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20according%20to%20EY%20chief%20economist%20Greg%20Daco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaco%20proposed%20three%20possible%20ways%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fisrael-hamas-war-palestine-shekel-dollar-dominance-currencies-dedollarization-investing-2023-10%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle-East%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20play%20out.%20The%20war%20thus%20far%20has%20sparked%20fears%20of%20a%20wider%20regional%20conflict%2C%20but%20markets%20so%20far%20have%20been%20relatively%20muted%20in%20their%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20severe%20outcome%20of%20the%20war%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Buncontained%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20Daco%20said%2C%20where%20the%20war%20escalates%20and%20could%20ultimately%20see%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20US%20or%20Iran%2C%20or%20both.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20situation%2C%20oil%20prices%20could%20immediately%20spike%20by%20%2450%20a%20barrel%2C%20notching%20%24150%20a%20barrel%20in%20late%202023%2C%20Daco%20warned.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20VIX%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20market%20volatility%20known%20as%20the%20stock%20market's%20fear%20gauge%2C%20could%20see%20a%20severe%20spike%2C%20jumping%20at%20by%20at%20least%2018%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20effects%20will%20ease%20into%20next%20year%2C%20Daco%20said%2C%20forecasting%20that%20oil%20prices%20could%20fall%20back%20to%20just%20%2410%20above%20the%20baseline%20forecast%20in%202024%2C%20while%20market%20volatility%20eases%20to%20four%20basis-points%20above%20the%20baseline%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2