20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CME%20FedWatch%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20outcomes%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20still%20involve%20a%20small%20spike%20in%20oil%20prices%20and%20market%20volatility%20over%20the%20near-term.%20In%20the%20best-case%20scenario%2C%20oil%20prices%20will%20only%20rise%20by%20%243%20a%20barrel%20by%20the%20VIX%20rises%20one%20basis-point%20higher%20than%20originally%20forecasted%20over%20the%20next%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20followed%20by%20the%20second-best%20relatively%20contained%20scenario%2C%20in%20which%20oil%20prices%20initially%20spike%20by%20%247%20a%20barrel%20before%20easing%20to%20%243%20higher%20than%20the%20baseline%20price%20forecast.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20VIX%20will%20spike%20five%20basis%20points%20in%20late%202023%2C%20before%20easing%20to%20just%20one%20basis-point%20higher%20than%20the%20baseline%20forecast%20by%20the%20end%20of%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hamas-outlook-oil-prices-economy-stock-market-volatility-inflation-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698088573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6238a910927f4a001886d222%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fisrael-hamas-outlook-oil-prices-economy-stock-market-volatility-inflation-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20%26quot%3Buncontained%26quot%3B%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20the%20US%20or%20Iran%20could%20become%20involved%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20surge%20in%20energy%20prices%20and%20market%20volatility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fisrael-hamas-outlook-oil-prices-economy-stock-market-volatility-inflation-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%2