08319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpresume-dil-dil-pakistan-england-great-brutally-trolls-babar-azam-and-co-after-cricket-world-cup-2023-loss-to-afghanistan-4508319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Remembering%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%3A%20The%20Man%20Who%20Found%20Sukoon%20in%20Junoon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDad%2C%20how%20will%20you%20remember%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20my%20father%2C%20as%20both%20of%20us%20cricket%20fanatics%2C%20sombrely%20sipped%20our%20'chai'%20having%20heard%20of%20the%20great%20cricketer's%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDad's%20reply%20was%20simple%20-%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Gavaskar%20was%20for%20India's%20batting%20then%2C%20Bedi%20was%20for%20India's%20bowling.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhy%2C%20I%20asked.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20skilled%2C%20fearless%2C%20competitive%20and%20inspiring.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20a%20damn%20good%20fighter%20pilot!'%26quot%3B%20For%20my%20dad%2C%20a%20retired%20Air%20Vice%20Marshal%2C%20that's%20a%20serious%20compliment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20among%20us%20to%20be%20loved.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20the%20first%20person%20to%20admit%20that%20about%20himself.%20Even%20his%20son%2C%20actor%20Angad%20Bedi%2C%20says%20this%20about%20his%20dad%20-%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20love%20him%2C%20hate%20him%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20way%20you%20can%20ignore%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi.%26quot%3B%20He%20believed%20that%20a%20person%20was%20nothing%20without%20complete%20integrity%20and%20honesty.%20His%20integrity%20saw%20him%20become%20one%20of%20India's%20greatest%20spin%20bowlers%20ever.%20His%20cutting%20honesty%20saw%20him%20courting%20controversy%20right%20through%20life.%20And%20I'm%20sure%20he%20would%20not%20have%20had%20it%20any%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20is%20made%20of%20the%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20and%20Bedi%20rivalry%2C%20both%20talismanic%20in%20many%20an%20Indian%20win%20and%20fightback.%20In%201979%2C%20Bedi%20was%20replaced%20by%20Sunny%20as%20India's%20captain%20and%20then%20dropped%20from%20the%20team%20as%20well.%20Bedi%20reportedly%20blamed%20Gavaskar%20for%20bringing%20his%20cricket%20career%20to%20an%20end.%20In%201990%2C%20Gavaskar%20called%20for%20Bedi's%20resignation%20as%20team%20coach%20after%20India%20lost%20a%20test%20series%20to%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20You%20Know%3F%20Bedi%20Named%20His%20Son%20after%20Sunil%20Gavaskar!%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20is%20simply%20not%20the%20complete%20picture.%20Writing%20in%20'The%20Sardar%20of%20Spin'%20%2C%20a%20book%20of%20essays%20curated%20by%20his%20daughter%20Neha%20and%20published%20to%20commemorate%20Bedi's%2075th%20birthday%2C%20Sunny%20reminds%20us%20of%20how%20Bedi%20named%20his%20son%2C%20back%20in%201971%20-%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20last%20Test%20match%20of%20India's%20triumphant%20West%20Indies%20tour%2C%20I%20was%20floored%20and%20honoured%20when%2C%20in%20Trinidad%2C%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20-%20who%20had%20become%20a%20father%20during%20the%20game%20-%20named%20his%20first%20born%2C%20Gavas%20Inder%20Singh.%26quot%3B%20Go%20figure!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunny%20added%20-%20%26quot%3BUntil%20Wasim%20Akram%20came%2C%20Bishan%20was%20the%20best%20left-hand%20bowler%20I%20had%20seen.%20One%20can%20now%20say%20that%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20is%20the%20best%20left-arm%20spinner%2C%20and%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20the%20best%20left-hand%20pacer.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Gaurav%20Kapoor%20in%20a%20video%20interview%2C%20Bedi%20said%20on%20his%20alleged%20bete%20noire%20-%20%26quot%3BGavaskar...%20bahut%20bada%20khiladi%20tha..%20imaan%20se%2C%20maine%20aisa%20khiladi%20duniya%20mein%20nahi%20dekha!%26quot%3B%20And%20that%2C%20pretty%20much%20sets%20the%20record%20straight%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBedi%20and%20the%20Spin%20Quartet%20-%20India's%20WMD!%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20cricket%20world%20where%20pace%20bowlers%20are%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20spear%20for%20every%20test%20playing%20nation%2C%20it%20was%20the%20genius%20of%20Mansur%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%2C%20India's%20captain%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20that%20turned%20spin%20bowling%20into%20India's%20WMD.%20Bedi%20acknowledges%20Pataudi's%20role%20in%20creating%20the%20legendary%20spin%20quartet%20of%20Bedi%2C%20Prasanna%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20Venkataraghavan%2C%20who%20between%20them%20played%20231%20test%20matches%20and%20claimed%20853%20wickets.%20Intriguingly%2C%20all%20four%20of%20them%20played%20in%20the%20same%20test%20match%20just%20once%2C%20in%20Birmingham%20against%20England%20in%201967.%20But%20with%20their%20array%20of%20unique%20skills%20-%20two%20off-spinners%20(Prasanna%20and%20Venkat)%2C%20a%20leg%20spinner%20(Chandra)%2C%20and%20Bedi%2C%20the%20left-arm%20spinner%2C%20they%20spun%20fear%20into%20the%20mind%20of%20every%20kind%20of%20batter%20around%20the%20globe.%20And%20within%20this%20quartet%20too%2C%20despite%20each%20competing%20for%20their%20place%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20there%20was%20great%20affection.%20Talking%20about%20his%20fellow%20spin%20wizards%2C%20Bedi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BErapalli%2C%20Venkat%20and%20Bhagwat%20were%20all%20very%20intelligent%2C%20all%20engineers!%20I%20was%20the%20only%203rd%20class%20graduate%20among%20them!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi's%20own%20prowess%20as%20a%20bowler%20was%20legendary%2C%20something%20I%20did%20not%20really%20witness.%20I%20was%20just%2011%20months%20old%20when%20he%20achieved%20his%20career-best%20figures%20of%207%2F98%20against%20Australia%20in%20Kolkata%20in%20December%201969.%20So%2C%20naturally%20Dad%20filled%20in%20the%20blanks%20-%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20was%20flying%20MiGs%20in%20Chandigarh%20then.%20We%20were%20gathered%20around%20my%20transistor%20listening%20to%20the%20commentary.%20Bedi%20had%20taken%209%20wickets%20in%20the%20previous%20match%20in%20Delhi.%20And%20then%207%20more%20in%20Calcutta!%20Classic%20Bedi%20mop%20up!%26quot%3B%20And%20just%20to%20underline%20that%20Bishan%20was%20as%20lethal%20in%20foreign%20conditions%2C%20his%20best%20match%20figures%20of%2010%2F194%2C%20came%20at%20Perth%2C%20Australia%2C%20on%20a%20pitch%20widely%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20pace-friendly%20in%20the%20world.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECricket's%20Great%20Controversialist!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20never%20easy%20to%20fully%20understand%20a%20person%20who%20has%20spent%20a%20large%20part%20of%20his%20life%20in%20the%20public%20glare.%20They%20get%20defined%20by%20their%20most%20famous%2C%20or%20even%20infamous%2C%20accomplishments.%20So%20it%20is%20with%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20as%20well.%20He%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20famous%20for%20his%20legendary%20deceptive%20spin%20bowling.%20His%20brave%20flighted%20deliveries%20would%20tempt%20batters%20into%20going%20for%20their%20shots%2C%20but%20would%20then%20dip%20suddenly%20and%20surprise%20even%20the%20best.%20While%20Bedi%20snared%20267%20wickets%20in%2067%20test%20matches%2C%20he%20also%20spoke%20his%20mind%20on%20the%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201976%2C%20as%20captain%2C%20he%20declared%20India's%20innings%20at%2097%2F5%20in%20Jamaica%20to%20protest%20against%20intimidatory%20bowling%20by%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20practically%20forfeiting%20the%20match.%20In%201978%20too%2C%20he%20forfeited%20an%20ODI%20match%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20citing%20partisan%20umpiring.%20He%20also%2C%20infamously%2C%20remained%20a%20critic%20of%20spin%20legend%20Muttiah%20Muralitharan's%20bowling%20action%3B%20right%20through%20the%20Lankan's%20career%2C%20he%20called%20it%20'chucking'.%20He%20has%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20IPL's%20'player%20auctions'%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20unseemly%20for%20cricketers%20to%20be%20'sold%20to%20the%20highest%20bidder'.%20In%201990%2C%20as%20coach%20of%20Team%20India%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20'dump'%20the%20team%20'in%20the%20sea'%20after%20they%20lost%20a%20match%20against%20Australia.%20Yes%2C%20the%20list%20is%20long%2C%20by%20Bedi's%20own%20admission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20explains%20this%3F%20First%2C%20Bedi%20always%20believed%20in%20speaking%20up%20for%20what%20he%20believed%20in%20-%20%26quot%3BChup%20rehna%20is%20a%20crime%20%26quot%3B'%20he%20said.%20He%20lamented%20the%20'fact'%20that%20'99.9%25%20of%20people%20in%20India%20sit%20on%20the%20fence'.%20Speaking%20up%20was%20central%20to%20Bedi's%20idea%20of%20integrity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20son%20gets%20it%20right.%20Speaking%20to%20Sportstar%20in%202017%20Angad%20said%20-%20'Anyone%20who%20follows%20Indian%20cricket%20closely%20would%20know%20that%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20is%20never%20a%20people-pleaser.%20Just%20like%20his%20bowling%20style%2C%20he%20loves%20being%20sharp%2C%20accurate%20and%20always%20in%20the%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20foreword%20of%20'The%20Sardar%20of%20Spin'%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20summed%20up%20Bedi%20aptly%20-%20%26quot%3BCritics%20would%20call%20Bishan%20paaji%20a%20rebel.%20Wrong.%20To%20me%2C%20he%20was%20a%20cricketer%20who%20knew%20his%20rights%20well.%20He%20stood%20up%20for%20the%20cricketers%2C%20fighting%20for%20better%20match%20fees%2C%20travel%20facilities%20and%20accommodation.%20He%20took%20on%20the%20DDCA..%20he%20did%20not%20hesitate%20to%20clash%20with%20BCCI%20officials%20when%20he%20thought%20they%20were%20not%20being%20fair...%20True%2C%20he%20suffered%20in%20the%20process%2C%20but%20always%20emerged%20with%20his%20head%20held%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Junoon'%20and%20'Sukoon'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeing%20driven%20by%20passion%20or%20by%20'Junoon'%20was%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi's%20way%20of%20life%2C%20on%20the%20field%2C%20off%20it%2C%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20and%20with%20his%20family.%20And%20paradoxically%2C%20as%20he%20explained%20to%20sports%20show%20host%20Gaurav%20Kapoor%2C%20it%20was%20this%20passion%20or%20'Junoon'%2C%20that%20led%20him%20towards%20'peace'%20or%20'Sukoon'%20-%20knowing%20that%20he%20has%20spoken%20up%20and%20stood%20by%20what%20he%20believed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Bedi%2C%20the%20honest%20and%20passionate%20pursuit%20of%20one's%20calling%20is%20what%20leads%20to%20true%20inner%20peace.%20And%20this%20ties%20up%20with%20his%20great%20love%20for%20Punjabi%20'kirtans'.%20He%20would%20listen%20raptly%20to%20'raagis'%20or%20singers%2C%20as%20they%20sang%20their%20devotional%20'kirtans'.%20In%20the%20'sadhna'%20or%20repeated%20practice%20of%20his%20singing%2C%20his%20vocation%2C%20Bedi%20saw%20himself%20in%20the%20'raagi'%20-%20as%20someone%20who%20lost%20himself%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20his%20passion%20-%20in%20Bedi's%20case%2C%20the%20love%20of%20spin%20bowling%2C%20and%20the%20love%20of%20cricket.%20Gosh%2C%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20will%20be%20missed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20commentator%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20Executive%20Producer%20of%20Investigations%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Projects%20at%20CNN-IBN%2C%20and%20is%20a%202-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698086520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fultdjs38_bishen-singh-bedi_625x300_23_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fremembering-bishan-singh-bedi-the-man-who-found-sukoon-in-junoon-4508325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20among%20us%20to%20be%20loved.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20the%20first%20person%20to%20admit%20that%20about%20himself.%20Even%20his%20son%20says%20this%20about%20his%20dad%20-%2