0He%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20has%20used%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20parliamentary%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20post%20questions%20from%20Dubai%20%E2%80%93%20a%20situation%2C%20if%20proved%2C%20will%20mean%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%20and%20lead%20to%20her%20suspension%20from%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20his%20actions%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20error%20of%20judgment%20and%20deeply%20regrettable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20he%20has%20embarrassed%20himself%20directly%20and%20%26quot%3Bmy%20company%20indirectly%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bincumbent%20on%20me%20to%20come%20forth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20allegation%20we%20prefer%20to%20come%20forward%20with%20the%20truth%20and%20that's%20what%20I%20have%20done%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20affidavit%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Parliamentary%20Ethics%20Committee.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20affidavit%20that%20made%20headlines%20last%20week%2C%20Mahua%20Moitra%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20%26quot%3Bheld%20a%20proverbial%20gun%26quot%3B%20to%20Mr%20Hiranandani's%20head%20and%20made%20him%20sign%20a%20white%20paper%20that%20was%20later%20%26quot%3Bleaked%20to%20the%20press%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDarshan%20Hiranandani%20has%20not%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20CBI%20or%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20or%20indeed%20by%20any%20investigative%20agency%20yet.%20Who%20then%20has%20he%20given%20this%20affidavit%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20use%20of%20her%20login%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey's%20call%20for%20an%20investigation%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20issued%20a%20strident%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequest%20NIC%20to%20please%20release%20ALL%20details%20of%20MPs%20publicly%