ians%20from%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20war%20crime%20according%20to%20international%20law%2C%20and%20a%20red%20line%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian%20leader%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20international%20community%20to%20criticise%20Israel%20for%20the%20targeting%20of%20civilian%20infrastructure%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20prohibition%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698081485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23224325%2FThe-Wire-51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-hamas-war-modi-speaks-with-jordans-king-abdullah-calls-for-early-resolution-of-crisis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jordan%20has%20the%20longest%20border%20with%20Israel%20and%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20nearly%20half%20of%20its%20population%20is%20of%20Palestinian%20descent.%20Unlike%20most%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%2C%20India%20has%20refrained%20from%20explicitly%20advocating%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20up%20to%20this%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-hamas-war-modi-speaks-with-jordans-king-abdullah-calls-for-early-resolution-of-crisis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NCLAT%20dismisses%20plea%20to%20initiate%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20Inox%20Wind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698081452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-05%2F15%2Ffull%2F1494872066-6986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Finterviews%2Fnclat-dismisses-plea-to-initiate-insolvency-proceedings-against-inox-wind-123102301059_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-member%20bench%20of%20the%20insolvency%20appellate%20tribunal%20also