%20oldest%20living%20dog%20and%20the%20oldest%20dog%20ever.%20He%20broke%20a%20record%20held%20by%20Australian%20cattle%20dog%20Bluey%2C%20who%20died%20at%2029%20years%20and%20five%20months%20in%201939.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67194721%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bobi's%20grand%20old%20age%20was%20validated%20by%20the%20Portuguese%20government's%20pet%20database%2C%20which%20is%20managed%20by%20the%20National%20Union%20of%20Veterinarians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-ever-bobi-dies-aged-31-760019%5C%22%3EGWR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bobi%20lived%20his%20entire%20life%20with%20Leonel%20Costa%20and%20his%20family%20in%20the%20rural%20village%20of%20Conqueiros%20in%20Portugal.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20an%20outhouse%20with%20three%20siblings%2C%20but%20Mr%20Costa%20said%20the%20puppies%20had%20to%20be%20put%20down%20as%20his%20family%20had%20too%20many%20animals.%20But%20somehow%20Bobi%20managed%20to%20escape%20and%20continued%20to%20live%20at%20the%20rural%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-nigerian-man-once-sold-a-fake-airport-to-a-brazilian-bank-for-242-million-read-his-story-4507135%5C%22%3EThis%20Nigerian%20Man%20Once%20Sold%20A%20%26quot%3BFake%20Airport%26quot%3B%20To%20A%20Brazilian%20Bank%20For%20%24242%20Million.%20Read%20His%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Costa%2C%20who%20was%20just%20eight%20when%20the%20dog%20was%20born%2C%20credited%20Bobi's%20long%20life%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bcalm%2C%20peaceful%20environment%26quot%3B%20he%20lived%20in%20%26quot%3Bfar%20from%20the%20cities%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20dog%20always%20ate%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20we%20ate%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20never%20chained%20up%20or%20put%20on%20a%20leash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20a%20scare%20in%202018%20when%20he%20was%20hospitalised%20after%20suddenly%20collapsing%20due%20to%20breathing%20difficulty%2C%20Mr%20Costa%20said%20that%20Bobi%20had%20enjoyed%20a%20relatively%20trouble-free%20life.%20But%20as%20he%20advanced%20in%20age%2C%20he%20became%20less%20mobile.%20He%20had%20even%20experienced%20trouble%20walking%20and%20worsening%20eyesight%20prior%20to%20his%20death%2C%20as%20per%20Mr%20Costa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBobi%20turned%2031%20in%20May%2C%20despite%20his%20breed%20having%20a%20typical%20life%20expectancy%20of%20between%2012%20and%2014%20years.%20%26quot%3BBobi%20had%20many%20fans%20around%20the%20globe%20-%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20100%2B%20people%20who%20showed%20up%20to%20his%2031st%20birthday%20party%20-%20and%20he%20will%20be%20sorely%20missed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20GWR%20wrote%20in%20its%20blog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698080580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2n20u0s8_oldest-dog-photo-guinness-1200_625x300_12_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbobi-worlds-oldest-dog-ever-dies-at-age-31-4508245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20oldest%20dog%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2031%20years%20and%20165%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbobi-worlds-oldest-dog-ever-dies-at-age-31-4508245%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbobi-worlds-oldest-dog-ever-dies-at-age-31-4508245%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbobi-worlds-oldest-dog-ever-dies-at-age-31-4508245%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airlines%20to%20operate%208.16%25%20more%20flights%20this%20winter%2C%20shows%20DGCA%20data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698080282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2