is%20'Not%20Just%20Unethical%20But%20Illegal'%3A%20Ex-Civil%20Servant%20EAS%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221501%2FThe-Wire-50.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20once%20again%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3EUnion%20government%E2%80%99s%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20senior%20government%20officers%20as%20%E2%80%9Crath%20prabharis%E2%80%9D%20who%20will%20propagate%20information%20on%20so-called%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20other%20provocations%20too%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98selfie-points%E2%80%99%20being%20assigned%20to%20government%2C%20civil%20and%20defence%20staff%20which%20have%20Modi%20in%20the%20frame.%20But%20IAS%20officers%20as%20%E2%80%9Crath%20prabharis%E2%80%9D%20have%20led%20ex-bureaucrats%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20express%20strong%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarma%20had%20first%20written%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20October%2021%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20commission%20must%20intervene%20and%20block%20this%20government%20order.%20These%20instructions%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20were%20against%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20which%20is%20in%20place%20in%20five%20states%20going%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221653%2Fimage.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221653%2Fimage.jpg%201120w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221653%2Fimage-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221653%2Fimage-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESelfie%20point%20at%20a%20Metro%20Station%20in%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Banjot%20Kaur%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20second%20letter%20sent%20on%20Monday%20(October%2023)%2C%20Sarma%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20ECI%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20his%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20a%20short%20interview%20with%20him%20on%20the%20latest%20in%20provocations%2C%20which%20appear%20to%20try%20and%20skew%20the%20level%20playing%20field%20which%20is%20a%20must%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20so%2C%20while%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20not%20in%20place%2C%202024%20polls%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20your%20primary%20objection%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20of%20government%20officers%20as%20Rath%20Prabharis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20objection%20is%20to%20the%20government%20asking%20its%20officers%20to%20showcase%20its%20achievements%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Model%20Code%20came%20into%20effect.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20violates%20the%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20earlier%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20unethical%20but%20is%20it%20also%20illegal%3F%20Can%20officers%20say%20no%20to%20the%20govt%20order%3F%20Should%20the%20Election%20Commission%20act%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20illegal%20as%20it%20violates%20the%20Model%20Code.%20Deploying%20public%20servants%20in%20activity%20likely%20to%20influence%20voters%20during%20elections%20violates%20the%20election%20law.%20Also%2C%20the%20civil%20services%20conduct%20rules%20prohibit%20civil%20servants%20from%20doing%20anything%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20unduly%20influence%20voters.%20A%20conscientious%20civil%20servant%20can%20point%20this%20out%2C%20say%20%E2%80%9Cno%E2%80%9D%20and%20refrain%20from%20taking%20part%20in%20such%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20Union%20ministers%20contesting%20Assembly%20elections.%20It%20is%20bizarre%20that%20their%20officers%20should%20be%20showcasing%20their%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20constituencies%20in%20which%20they%20will%20contest%20when%20the%20Code%20is%20in%20force.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20it%20should%20attract%20disqualification%20of%20such%20candidates%2C%20for%20deploying%20their%20officers%20and%20public%20resources%2C%20when%20the%20Moral%20Code%20is%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20ought%20to%20have%20acted%20on%20it%20immediately%2C%20instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20citizens%20and%20political%20parties%20pointing%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20a%20similar%20transgression%20in%20the%20past%20that%20this%20brings%20to%20mind%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20do%20not%20remember%20such%20an%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20options%20exist%20for%20citizens%20if%20the%20EC%20does%20not%20take%20note%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20EC%20fails%20to%20act%2C%20courts%20are%20the%20only%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698079856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221501%2FThe-Wire-50.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fias-officers-as-rath-prabharis-is-not-just-unethical-but-illegal-ex-civil-servant-eas-sarma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deploying%20public%20servants%20in%20activity%20likely%20to%20influence%20voters%20during%20elections%20violates