anks%20and%20offers%20handsome%20rewards%20to%20the%20toppers.%20They%20use%20children%20as%20a%20commodity%20and%20their%20parents%20put%20all%20their%20hopes%20and%20pressures%20on%20their%20children.%20But%2C%20what%20can%20a%20child%20do%20in%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20having%20a%20capacity%20or%20the%20facility%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20children%20get%20flustered.%20Even%20adults%20struggle%20with%20managing%20stress%2C%20how%20will%20the%20young%20kids%20fare%20then%3F%20Everyone%20is%20a%20competitor%20and%20the%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20wards%20to%20Kota%2C%20where%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20have%20very%20high%20fees.%20Different%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20Kota%20coaching%20market%20generates%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20crores%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20(name%20changed)%20came%20to%20Kota%20in%20June%202023.%20The%2016-year-old%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%20a%20small%20grocery%20store%20in%20Kanpur%20and%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20as%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20become%20one.%20He%20was%20raised%20with%20the%20expectations%20of%20studying%20in%20an%20IIT%20and%20being%20the%20harbinger%20of%20hope%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20many%20friends%2C%20he%20says%2C%20and%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20adjust%20to%20this%2024%C3%977%20study%20environment%20where%20relaxation%20is%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20away%20from%20home%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20an%20introvert.%20I%20was%20a%20topper%20in%20my%20school%2C%20but%20so%20is%20everyone%20else%20here.%20The%20pressure%20is%20a%20lot.%20My%20parents%20have%20borrowed%20money%20to%20send%20me%20here%20and%20I%20know%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20all%20this%20to%20get%20me%20into%20an%20IIT.%20But%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20get%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20the%20documentary%20'An%20Engineered%20Dream'.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-768x402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-252008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20documentary%20%E2%80%98An%20Engineered%20Dream%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20race%20to%20the%20top%2C%20mental%20health%20is%20often%20ignored.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20work%20of%20the%20police%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%2C%20counsellors%20and%20teachers%20like%20Singh%20is%20crucial.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20may%20be%20life%20saving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20over%2080%2C000%20students%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20Thakur.%20They%20interact%20with%20teachers%2C%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20PG%20owners%2C%20mess%20staff%20and%20Thakur%20himself%20spends%20many%20evenings%20at%20different%20hostels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20positive%20change.%20Now%2C%20students%20know%20that%20they%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20us.%20Hostel%20wardens%20and%20mess%20staff%20are%20the%20most%20important%20link%20for%20us.%20They%20can%20observe%20any%20small%20change%20in%20a%20child%2C%20and%20we%20ask%20them%20to%20report%20it%20to%20us%20immediately.%20Even%20what