State%20Education%20Policy%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20filling%20vacancies%2C%20Sudhakar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hijab%20issue%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20discussion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20want%20to%20raise%20objections%20to%20small%20things%2C%20but%20we%20cannot%20infringe%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20people.%20Even%20in%20NEET%2C%20candidates%20%5Bare%5D%20allowed%20to%20wear%20hijab%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%3Cem%3E%20TOI%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20secular%20country.%20People%20are%20free%20to%20dress%20however%20they%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fkarnataka-permits-hijab-at-exam-centres-sparks-row-2452361-2023-10-22%5C%22%3Etold%20India%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20there%20was%20some%20criticism%2C%20he%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1716334710417420346%5C%22%3Emedia%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20the%20people%20who%20are%20protesting%20should%20verify%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20NEET%20exam.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20are%20they%20making%20an%20issue%20out%20of%20this%E2%80%A6People%20are%20allowed%20to%20wear%20hijabs%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%E2%80%99s%20comments%20are%20significant%20because%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20banned%20students%20from%20wearing%20hijabs%20to%20government%20schools%20in%20early%202022.%20The%20issue%2C%20which%20began%20after%20the%20Government%20PU%20College%20in%20Udupi%20barred%20hijab-wearing%20girls%20from%20entering%20the%20classroom%2C%20snowballed%20into%20a%20statewide%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkarnataka-hijab-case-verdict%5C%22%3Eupheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20in%20March%202022%2C%20which%20held%20that%20hijab%20was%20not%20an%20ess