E%E2%80%94%20Dalit%20Times%20%7C%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B8%20(%40DalitTime)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDalitTime%2Fstatus%2F1714499999583883711%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20MA%20student%20and%20All%20India%20Student%20Association%20(AISA)%20unit%20president%20Vivek%20Kumar%20believes%20the%20October%2017%20attack%20stems%20from%20a%20place%20of%20discrimination%20and%20bias%20towards%20marginalised%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20the%20chief%20proctor%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20all%20such%20incidents%20in%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20leading%20the%20protest%20for%20a%20number%20of%20reasons%20and%20we%20had%20some%20demands%20which%20in%20my%20opinion%20were%20quite%20reasonable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20the%20chief%20proctor%20became%20absolutely%20furious%20and%20started%20hitting%20me.%20I%20was%20shocked%2C%20I%20had%20not%20expected%20that.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20students%20along%20with%20Kumar%20marched%20up%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20and%20spent%20eight%20hours%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20police%20to%20lodge%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20Singh%2C%20but%20were%20unsuccessful.%20%E2%80%9CFormer%20IPS%20officer%20Amitabh%20Thakur%20sir%20was%20also%20accompanying%20us%20but%20even%20with%20his%20help%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20police%20to%20lodge%20an%20FIR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protest%20that%20got%20the%20chief%20proctor%20riled%20up%20was%20part%20of%20an%20agitation%20which%20gained%20momentum%20when%20the%20university%20implemented%20a%20staggering%20400%25%20fee%20hike%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThree%20students%20who%20were%20leading%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20fee%20increase%20%E2%80%93%20Ajay%20Yadav%20Samrat%2C%20Satyam%20Kushwaha%2C%20and%20Jeetendra%20Dhanraj%20%E2%80%93%20were%20suspended%20and%20jailed%20about%20three%20months%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20two%20more%20students%20Harendra%20Yadav%20and%20Manish%20Kumar%20had%20been%20suspended%20for%20other%20reasons.%20Harendra%20Yadav%20is%20now%20not%20even%20being%20permitted%20to%20sit%20for%20exams%20which%20goes%20against%20the%20basic%20rights%20of%20students.%20In%20the%20history%20of%20this%20institution%20even%20if%20someone%20has%20been%20in%20jail%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20released%20on%20parole%20to%20come%20and%20sit%20for%20exams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23170243%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-20-at-6.36.51-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23170243%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-20-at-6.36.51-PM.jpeg%20972w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23170243%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-20-at-6.36.51-PM-300x222.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStudent%20bodies%20protest%20against%20the%20assault%20on%20Vivek%20Kumar%20at%20Allahabad%20University%20and%20demand%20the%20suspension%20of%20proctor%20Rakesh%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demands%20at%20the%20latest%20protest%2C%20Kumar%20said%2C%20were%20that%20of%20the%20release%20of%20the%20three%20students%20from%20jail%2C%20lifting%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspension%20of%20all%20students%2C%20and%20permission%20to%20sit%20for%20exams%20for%20Harendra%20Yadav%2C%20among%20other%20demands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20one%20more%20demand%20has%20been%20added%20and%20that%20is%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20proctor%20Rakesh%20Singh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVive%20Kumar%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Baramadpur%2C%20said%20this%20is%20not%20his%20first%20encounter%20with%20proctor%20Rakesh%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20lived%20in%20the%20hostel%2C%20the%20superintendent%20was%20Rakesh%20Singh.%20During%20the%20first%20week%20when%20the%20beds%20were%20allotted%20and%20the%20list%20came%20out%2C%20it%20showed%20only%20nine%20out%20of%20112%20were%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe.%20When%20I%20questioned%20it%20and%20said%20it%20should%20be%20at%20least%2025-26%20students%20according%20to%20the%20reservation%2C%20he%20got%20very%20angry%20and%20warned%20me%20to%20keep%20my%20concerns%20to%20myself%20or%20he%E2%80%99d%20remove%20me%20from%20the%20hostel%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumar%20believes%20the%20hostel%20incident%20had%20the%20proctor%20harbouring%20a%20grudge%20against%20him%20which%20has%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20he%20dislikes%20me%20for%20taking%20a%20stand%20on%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20seen%20a%20pattern%20of%20discrimination%20not%20just%20towards%20Dalits%20but%20also%20towards%20students%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20minorities%2C%20and%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20barred%20from%20entering%20the%20university%20premises%20on%20weekends%20which%20is%20highly%20inconvenient%20for%20them%2C%20they%20just%20want%20to%20study.%20The%20authorities%20cite%20the%20issue%20of%20security%20as%20reason%20but%20if%20that%E2%80%99s%20so%20then%20something%20should%20be%20done%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20access%20to%20the%20library%2C%20Kumar%20says%2C%20has%20also%20been%20a%20big%20point%20of%20protest%20with%20students%20demanding%20the%20library%20be%20made%20open%20and%20accessible%2024%20hours%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20library%20currently%20closes%20at%206%20pm%20which%20means%20some%20students%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20proper%20place%20to%20study%20after%20that%20time.%20We%20have%20been%20fighting%20to%20get%20the%20hours%20increased%20but%20no%20one%E2%80%99s%20heard%20our%20plea.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deteriorating%20state%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20unsanitary%20toilets%2C%20and%20impure%20drinking%20water%20are%20some%20other%20points%20which%20have%20often%20been%20raised%20by%20concerned%20students%20but%20all%20requests%2C%20Kumar%20says%2C%20have%20fallen%20on%20deaf%20ears.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20it%20seems%20that%20if%20you%20raise%20your%20voice%20against%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20things%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20either%20be%20suspended%20or%20jailed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20history%20of%20this%20university%2C%20there%20has%20always%20been%20some%20or%20the%20other%20issue%20that%20students%20have%20been%20dissatisfied%20with%20and%20have%20protested%20against%2C%20and%20authorities%20have%20heard%20their%20demands%20and%20often%20tried%20to%20resolve%20issues.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20there%20has%20been%20growing%20intolerance%20towards%20protests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20of%20Lucknow%20University%20and%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20have%20shown%20solidarity%20with%20Vivek%20Kumar%20and%20have%20come%20out%20in%20huge%20numbers%2C%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20accused%20Rakesh%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELucknow%20University%20student%20and%20National%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20of%20India%20(NSUI)%20student%20representative%20Vishal%20Singh%20said%20several%20students%20from%20AISA%2C%20NSUI%2C%20and%20other%20unions%20gathered%20on%20campus%20on%20October%2018%20to%20condemn%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdisgusting%20assault%E2%80%9D%20by%20Rakesh%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20see%20some%20action%20being%20taken%2C%20authorities%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20case%20lightly%20just%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20Dalit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lucknow%20student%20believes%20while%20Allahabad%20University%20and%20Lucknow%20University%20are%20two%20different%20institutions%2C%20the%20issues%20faced%20by%20the%20students%20are%20quite%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20out%20against%20anything%20now.%20Just%20to%20give%20an%20example%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20hostel%20were%20told%20that%20if%20they%20posted%20anything%20on%20social%20media%20that%20shows%20the%20university%20in%20a%20bad%20light%20then%20they%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20fine%20and%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20vacate%20the%20hostel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20says%20students%20are%20always%20being%20issued%20show-cause%20notices%20for%20various%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVishal%20Singh%20joined%20Vivek%20Kumar%20and%20other%20students%20in%20their%20protest%20in%20Allahabad%20on%20Thursday%20last%20week%20and%20plans%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20city%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20vice-chancellor%20Sangita%20Srivastava%E2%80%99s%20office%20and%20registrar%20N.K.%20Shukla%20and%20is%20still%20waiting%20for%20a%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698062446000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23165034%2FThe-Wire-48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fallahabad-university-dalit-student-vivek-kumar-assaulted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Students%20from%20Lucknow%20University%20and%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20have%20extended%20solidarity%20to%20the%20assaulted%20student.%20Police%20yet%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20despite%20repeated%20requests%20from%20student%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fallahabad-university-dalit-student-vivek-kumar-assaulted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ONGC%20wins%20bid%20to%20acquire%20PTC%20India's%20wind%20power%20unit%20for%20Rs%20925%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698062376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F04%2Ffull%2F1680579212-9196.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fongc-wins-bid-to-acquire-ptc-india-s-wind-power-unit-for-rs-925-crore-123102300625_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20stock%20exchange%20filing%2C%20India's%20top%20oil%20and%20gas%20producer%20said%20it%20has%20over%20the%20years%20diversified%20into%20the%20petrochemicals%20and%20power%20business%20besides%20growing%20its%20core%20business%20of%20finding%20hydrocarbons%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fongc-wins-bid-to-acquire-ptc-i