2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shortages%20in%20semiconductors%20and%20chips%20needed%20to%20manufacture%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20mean%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fone-nation-one-poll-election-commission-says-it-needs-up-to-a-years-lead-time-for-evms-vvpats-8995310%2F%5C%22%3Eup%20to%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20time%20is%20needed%20to%20be%20ready%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20source%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20election%20commission%20(EC)%20felt%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdefinite%20lead%20time%20of%20up%20to%20a%20year%20would%20be%20required%20for%20ramping%20up%20the%20voting%20machine%20production%20lines%E2%80%9D%20given%20the%20current%20commitments%20of%20government%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cshortage%20of%20semiconductors%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20has%20further%20messed%20up%20the%20timelines%20for%20EVM%20procurement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESemiconductors%20and%20chips%20are%20also%20required%20to%20produce%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20machines%2C%20which%20make%20up%20part%20of%20a%20voting%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20EC%20told%20a%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20use%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20its%20budget%20for%20procuring%20EVMs%20due%20to%20semiconductor%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20reportedly%20raised%20the%20shortages%20issue%20to%20the%20eight-member%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20examining%20the%20feasibility%20of%20simultaneous%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3EThis%20panel%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20as%20well%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20have%20endorsed%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20simultaneous%20elections.%20This%20idea%20is%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20is%20also%20examining%20the%20feasibility%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Flaw-panel-readies-report-on-simultaneous-polls-likely-timelines-for-2024-and-2029-8957758%2F%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20frame%20tentative%20timelines%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%20and%202029%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-one-leader-one-faith-one-business-house%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20One%20Leader%2C%20One%20Faith%2C%20One%20Business%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20suggest%20having%20some%20assembly%20elections%20along%20with%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20ultimately%20all%20assembly%20elections%20with%20the%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20its%20report%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20predecessor%20(the%2021st%20Law%20Commission)%20took%20a%20gander%20at%20the%20issue%20of%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%202018%20but%20last-minute%20disagreements%20resulted%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fwhy-law-commission-didnt-submit-final-report-on-modis-one-nation-one-election-goal%2F108931%2F%5C%22%3Ereleasing%20a%20draft%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20a%20final%20report%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdnbbsr.s3waas.gov.in%2Fs3ca0daec69b5adc880fb464895726dbdf%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F2022092614.pdf%5C%22%3EIt%20supported%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20doing%20so%20will%20save%20public%20money%2C%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20administrative%20machinery%20and%20ensure%20better%20implementation%20of%20government%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20acknowledged%20that%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20possible%20within%20the%20existing%20framework%20of%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20constitutional%20amendments%20would%20be%20inevitable%20for%20the%20idea%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20issues%20involved%2C%20it%20is%20desirable%20to%20have%20further%20discussions%20and%20examination%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20involving%20all%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20once%20again%2C%20before%20making%20final%20recommendations%20to%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20its%20draft%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20its%20term%20ended%20before%20a%20final%20recommendation%20could%20be%20made%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20costs%20of%20Rs%205%2C200%20crore%20and%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%20will%20have%20to%20be%20met%20in%20order%20to%20arrange%20for%20the%20increased%20number%20of%20voting%20machines%20required%20to%20hold%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%202024%20and%202029%20respectively%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20citing%20EC%20estimates%20given%20to%20the%20law%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20this%20was%20also%20factoring%20in%20the%20projected%20increase%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20population%20by%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20polling%20stations%20across%20India%20will%20also%20increase%20%E