%2Famp%2Fsouth-china-sea-us-warns-china-of-intervention-after-collision-with-ships-from-philippines-in-contested-waters-12990877%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsouth-china-sea-us-warns-china-of-intervention-after-collision-with-ships-from-philippines-in-contested-waters-12990877%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Irreparable%20Damage%20to%20Democratic%20Values'%20if%20EC%20Doesn't%20Act%20Against%20'Rath%20Prabharis'%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20once%20again%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3EUnion%20government%E2%80%99s%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20senior%20government%20officers%20as%20%E2%80%9Crath%20prabharis%E2%80%9D%20who%20will%20spread%20informations%20on%20the%20alleged%20achievements%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarma%20had%20first%20written%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20October%2021%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20commission%20must%20intervene%20and%20block%20this%20government%20order.%20These%20instructions%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20were%20against%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%20Former%20IAS%20officer%20M.G.%20Devasahayam%20had%20endorsed%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20second%20letter%20sent%20on%20Monday%20(October%2023)%2C%20Sarma%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20ECI%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20his%20complaint.%20He%20pointed%20out%20four%20relating%20issues%2C%20including%20saying%20that%20public%20servants%20engaging%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20activity%20had%20the%20power%20to%20influence%20voters%20and%20electoral%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%2C%20Sarma%20argued%2C%20had%20a%20duty%20to%20act%20on%20the%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Commission%20fails%20to%20discharge%20its%20responsibilities%20envisaged%20under%20Article%20324%20and%20the%20relevant%20election%20laws%2C%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20amount%20to%20causing%20irreparable%20damage%20to%20the%20democratic%20values%20that%20lie%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20his%20full%20letter%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%20Former%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShri%20A%20C%20Pandey%3Cbr%3E%20Election%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShri%20Arun%20Goel%3Cbr%3E%20Election%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDear%20S%2FShri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2F%20Pandey%2F%20Goel%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20write%20this%20in%20continuation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F10%2Fdifferent-ministries-of-the-central-government-have-possibly-infringed-the-model-code-of-conduct%2F%5C%22%3Emy%20letter%20of%20October%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20which%20I%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20instructions%20issued%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%2C%20vide%20F.no.%201-28047%2F8%2F2023%20dated%2017-10-2023%20and%20other%20Ministries%20to%20nominate%20senior%20officers%20as%20%E2%80%9CDistrict%20Rath%20Praharis%E2%80%9D%20under%20their%20purview%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eshowcase%2Fcelebrate%20achievements%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20the%20NDA%20government%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%E2%80%99%C2%A0from%2020th%20November%202023%20to%2025th%20January%202024%E2%80%B3%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20State%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20brazenly%20violate%20the%C2%A0Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20for%20those%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20taken%20due%20cognizance%20of%20my%20complaint%20and%20acted%20as%20it%20should%2C%20as%20an%20independent%20authority%20under%20the%20Constitution%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20said%20elections%20are%20conducted%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20related%20issues%2C%20as%20indicated%20below%2C%20on%20which%20I%20would%20call%20upon%20the%20ECI%20to%20act%20immediately%20and%C2%A0unhesitatingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Public%20servants%20taking%20part%20in%20any%20activity%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20influence%20the%20voters%20in%20an%20election%20violates%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%20and%20the%20corresponding%20conduct%20rules%20of%20the%20other%20Central%20and%20All%20India%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20Under%20Section%20171C%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ewhoever%20voluntarily%20interferes%20or%20attempts%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20free%20exercise%20of%20any%20electoral%20right%20commits%20the%20offence%20of%20undue%20influence%20at%20an%20election%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C.%C2%A0%C2%A0For%20any%20public%20authority%20to%20coerce%20public%20servants%20into%20such%20activity%20is%20punishable%20not%20only%20under%20the%20relevant%20election%20laws%20but%20also%20under%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20Office%20Memorandum%20No.25%2F44%2F49%2FEsts.%20dated%2010th%20October%201949%20states%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%20%3Cem%3EAttention%20is%20invited%20to%20the%20scope%20of%20Rule%2023(I)%20of%20the%20Government%20Servants%E2%80%99%20Conduct%20Rules%20which%20lays%20down%20that%20no%20Government%20servant%20shall%20take%20part%20in%2C%20subscribe%20in%20aid%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20way%2C%20any%20political%20movement%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C.%20These%20instructions%20assume%20particular%20relevance%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20concern%20expressed%20by%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20At%20least%20four%20Union%20Ministers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Flok-sabha%2Findia%2F18-mps-including-4-union-ministers-bjps-star-studded-lineup-for-state-showdowns%2Farticleshow%2F104290879.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%20to%20be%20contesting%20the%20ensuing%20State%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Deploying%20Central%20government%20officers%20in%20activity%20that%20amounts%20to%20canvassing%20for%20the%20ruling%20political%20parties%20in%20elections%20they%20are%20contesting%20would%20clearly%20attract%20disqualification%20under%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20election%20laws%2C%20which%20the%20ECI%20should%20examine%20urgently.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20precedent%20set%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20by%20issuing%20the%20said%20instructions%20to%20its%20officers%20to%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eshowcase%2Fcelebrate%20achievements%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20the%20NDA%20government%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra'%E2%80%9D%20is%20likely%20to%20incentivise%20the%20political%20leadership%20in%20each%20State%20that%20will%20go%20for%20Assembly%20elections%20shortly%20to%20do%20likewise%20and%20instruct%20its%20own%20officers%20to%20canvass%20for%20them%2C%20leading%20to%20anarchy%20and%20erosion%20of%20democratic%20values%20that%20are%20central%20to%20the%20electoral%20system%20envisaged%20in%20our%20Constitution.%20The%20Commission%20cannot%20afford%20to%20remain%20passive%20and%20become%20an%20abettor%20of%20such%20a%20potentially%20dangerous%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMay%20I%20call%20upon%20the%20ECI%20to%20act%20urgently%20on%20these%20concerns%20and%20act%20without%20hesitation%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20no%20political%20party%20gets%20an%20undue%20advantage%20in%20the%20ensuing%20State%20Assembly%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Commission%20fails%20to%20discharge%20its%20responsibilities%20envisaged%20under%20Article%20324%20and%20the%20relevant%20election%20laws%2C%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20amount%20to%20causing%20irreparable%20damage%C2%A0to%20the%20democratic%20values%20that%20lie%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20circulating%20this%20letter%20widely%20for%20the%20public%20to%20discuss%20and%20debate%20the%20above%20concerns%20and%20the%20role%20that%20the%20Commission%20ought%20to%20play%20as%20an%C2%A0independent%20Constitutional%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegards%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%20Visakhapatnam%3Cbr%3E%2023-10-2023%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698051615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feas-sarma-letter-eci-rath-prabharis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20once%20again%20on%20the%20Union%20government's%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feas-sarma-letter-eci-rath-prabharis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sculpture%20commemorating%20alligator%20sewer%20myth%20unveiled%20in%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698049860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-alligator-new-york_6332238.jpg%3F20231023104944%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%26quot%3Bmasterpiece%26quot%3B%20sculpture%20has%20been%20unveiled%20in%20New%20York%20City%20paying%20homage%20to%20one%20of%20its%20most%20famous%20urban%20legends%20-%20alligators%20living%20in%20the%20sewers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20To%20Make%20Of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Opposition%20to%20Digitisation%20of%20Land%20Records%20in%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20digitised%20land%20records%20has%20become%20an%20election%20issue%20in%20Telangana%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20promising%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20land%20registry%20portal%2C%20%E2%80%9CDharani%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Congress%20has%20been%20very%20critical%20of%20land%20digitisation%2C%20saying%20that%20many%20farmers%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20error-prone%20process.%20In%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Telangana%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20promised%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20portal%20and%20claimed%20that%20digitisation%20was%20used%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20take%20away%20agricultural%20lands%20for%20government%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharani%20was%20made%20the%20only%20authentic%20source%20for%20land%20records%20in%202020%2C%20when%20Telangana%20passed%20a%20new%20revenue%20Act.%20The%20records%20on%20the%20land%20registry%20became%20mandatory%20for%20farmers%20to%20apply%20for%20crop%20loans%20and%20to%20receive%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%20under%20schemes%20like%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu.%20Any%20error%20in%20recording%20the%20land%20details%20would%20harm%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20access%20welfare%20or%20participate%20in%20economic%20processes%20linked%20to%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20India%20to%20push%20for%20the%20linking%20of%20land%20records%20to%20Aadhaar%20and%20digitise%20land%20records%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpurified%E2%80%9D%20land%20registry.%20This%20process%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20case%20of%20non-agricultural%20lands%20in%20the%20Telangana%20high%20court%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Ftelangana-hc-directs-state-not-to-insist-aadhaar-for-uploading-property-details-165474%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estopped%20Aadhaar%20linking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20land%20records%20as%20it%20can%20only%20be%20allowed%20for%20subsidies%20and%20is%20in%20contravention%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment.%20As%20farmers%20with%20agricultural%20lands%20benefit%20from%20different%20welfare%20subsidies%2C%20the%20linking%20of%20Aadhaar%20and%20agricultural%20land%20records%20continues%20unopposed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20land%20digitisation%20process%20%E2%80%93%20like%20any%20other%20digitisation%20process%20%E2%80%93%20is%20prone%20to%20software%20and%20data%20errors%2C%20fraud%20and%20governance%20problems.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20Aadhaar%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20making%20any%20software%20mandatory%20and%20the%20only%20source%20of%20verifiable%20information%20has%20brought%20challenges%20to%20normal%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20push%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fesign-can-do-to-land-markets-what-demat-did-to-equity-if-centre-and-state-come-together%2F1164167%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edematerialisation%20of%20government%20documents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20replacing%20them%20with%20centralised%20databases%20to%20facilitate%20easier%20market%20transactions.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Dharani%2C%20this%20is%20done%20through%20the%20issual%20of%20an%20electronic%20record%20of%20the%20land%20title%20and%20giving%20access%20to%20this%20data%20to%20bankers%20and%20other%20market%20actors.%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadex.org.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAgricultural%20Data%20Exchange%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20built%20in%20collaboration%20with%20IISc%20Bangalore%20and%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20is%20a%20place%20where%20these%20ideas%20of%20data%20exchange%20with%20market%20actors%20to%20facilitate%20farmer%20and%20land%20data%20sharing%20are%20being%20carried%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20recent%20research%20paper%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fjoac.12556%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIllegibly%20legible%3A%20Outcomes%20of%20a%20land%20records%20modernisation%20programme%20in%20South%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3Cspan%3E%20by%20economists%20Ramkumar%20R.%20and%20Padmini%20Ramesh%20details%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20digitisation%20of%20land%20records%20for%20Dharani.%20It%20gives%20a%20historical%20background%20of%20the%20digitisation%20of%20land%20in%20Telangana%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20errors%20were%20encountered%20with%20the%20process%20and%20how%20the%20revenue%20department%20addresses%20these%20challenges.%20The%20paper%20captures%20the%20scale%20and%20intensity%20of%20problems%20encountered%20with%20Dharani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20complicated%20disputes%20around%20land%20records%20mutation%2C%20updation%2C%20errors%2C%20fraud%20and%20purity%20of%20land%20titles%20have%20risen.%20The%20corruption%20centred%20around%20land%20registrations%20is%20well%20known%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20digitisation%20will%20somehow%20fix%20this%20has%20become%20a%20myth%20for%20the%20regular%20farmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharani%20has%20become%20an%20instrument%20where%20land%20titles%20automatically%20changed%20overnight%20with%20digitisation%2C%20not%20only%20due%20to%20errors%20or%20fraud%20by%20officials%20but%20also%20in%20scenarios%20where%20the%20state%20wanted%20to%20acquire%20land%20for%20development%20projects.%20In%20multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fcurrent-affairs%2F251222%2Fkcrs-govt-to-face-farmers-anger-over-land-acquisition.html%5C%22%3Ereported%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20updated%20land%20records%20on%20Dharani%20to%20indicate%20farmers%E2%80%99%20land%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Industrial%20and%20Infrastructure%20Corporation%20(TSIIC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x509.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20of%20the%20Dharani%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20digitisation%2C%20the%20state%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20arbitrarily%20change%20ownership%20of%20land%20and%20take%20it%20away%20with%20no%20recourse%20for%20the%20landowner.%20This%20ability%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of.%20the%20Telangana%20government%20acquiring%20land%20while%20subverting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA2013-30.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Right%20To%20Fair%20Compensation%20And%20Transparency%20In%20Land%20Acquisition%2C%20Rehabilitation%20And%20Resettlement%20Act%2C%202013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20not%20pay%20fair%20compensation.%20This%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1037993%2Fhow-telangana-subverted-indias-land-acquisition-law%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextensively%20written%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20by%20Faustina%20Johnson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fkcr-lambasts-detractors-of-dharani-asks-farmers-to-decide%2Farticle66939018.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecountering%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20leaders%E2%80%99%20claims%20by%20assuring%20people%20that%20land%20records%20can%20only%20be%20changed%20with%20Aadhaar%20biometrics.%20All%20the%20land%20records%20of%20Dharani%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20on%20a%20blockchain%2C%20according%20to%20various%20Telangana%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblockchaindistrict.telangana.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsites%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20actual%20evidence%20this%20was%20carried%20out%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20current%20errors%20in%20the%20system%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20Aadhaar%20in%20the%20land%20digitisation%20process%20is%20something%20of%20a%20mystery%20with%20no%20actual%20design%20details%20of%20the%20land%20registry%20available%20for%20anyone%20to%20understand%20the%20system.%20But%20what%20is%20not%20made%20clear%20to%20the%20general%20population%20is%20that%20Aadhaar%20usage%20is%20not%20actually%20used%20for%20identification%2C%20authentication%20or%20updation%20through%20eKYC.%20Instead%2C%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcca.gov.in%2FeSign.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-Sign%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20being%20used%20to%20digitally%20sign%20the%20land%20records%20before%20patta%20passbooks%20are%20issued%20through%20Dharani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20e-Sign%20system%20itself%20functions%20and%20what%20safeguards%20are%20being%20provided%20to%20citizens.%20The%20Aadhaar-based%20biometric%20authentication%20system%20is%20broken%2C%20with%20people%20able%20to%20clone%20biometrics%20and%20use%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20to%20commit%20fraudulent%20withdrawals%20by%20using%20the%20Aadhaar%20Enabled%20Payment%20System%20(AEPS).%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20state%20that%20can%20take%20away%20land%20%E2%80%93%20anyone%20with%20access%20to%20the%20land%20registry%20with%20details%20of%20your%20Aadhaar%20number%20and%20biometrics%20can%20potentially%20take%20your%20land%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Act%20making%20Aadhaar%20mandatory%20for%20property%20registration%2C%20this%20process%20is%20going%20to%20be%20scaled%20across%20India.%20Aadhaar%20is%20being%20shown%20as%20a%20way%20to%20handle%20estate%20management%20of%20claims%20over%20property%20after%20the%20death%20of%20an%20individual.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20this%20will%20happen%20at%20this%20stage.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Dharani%20too%2C%20the%20details%20of%20dependents%20of%20the%20property%20owner%20were%20collected%20to%20facilitate%20estate%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20promise%20of%20the%20immutability%20of%20land%20records%20that%20has%20been%20guaranteed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20blockchain%2C%20cleaning%20up%20and%20purifying%20records%20with%20Aadhaar%20linking%20are%20all%20technological%20myths%20if%20the%20systems%20are%20broken%20by%20design%20with%20tall%20claims%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20hold%20up.%20Indians%20deserve%20a%20better%20digitisation%20process%20with%20actual%20accountability%20instead%20of%20mere%20claims.%20While%20the%20Congress%20always%20defended%20Aadhaar%20for%20welfare%2C%20it%20now%20seems%20to%20have%20caught%20on%20to%20other%20issues%20of%20the%20digitisation%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698049857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20tall%20claims%20about%20purity%20of%20records%2C%20the%20Dharani%20land%20registry%20portal%20has%20been%20riddled%20with%20errors%20and%20cases%20of%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20oldest%20dog%20ever%20dies%20-%20as%20owner%20reveals%20secret%20to%20his%20long%20life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698049380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F05%2F70x70%2Fimage_6156855.jpg%3F20230516100400%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-dies-aged-31-12990846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20oldest%20dog%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8414%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-dies-aged-31-12990846%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-dies-aged-31-12990846%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-dies-aged-31-12990846%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Temple%20Board%20Says%20No%20to%20RSS%20Drills%2C%20Training%20on%20Temple%20Premises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23122455%2FTemple_in_Kerala.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Travancore%20Devaswom%20Board%20(TDB)%20has%20asked%20all%20temples%20under%20its%20control%20to%20not%20allow%20mass%20drills%20or%20any%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Ft