0occasionally%2C%20I%20would%20have%20this%20urge%20to%20go%20live%20near%20wildlife.%20So%20I%20always%20knew%20I%20would%20end%20up%20living%20someplace%20near%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20the%20time%20came%20to%20choose%20a%20place%2C%20Sunando%20chose%20the%20epicentre%20of%20breathtaking%20landscape%20and%20thriving%20wildlife%20%E2%80%94%20Corbett%2C%20where%20he%20currently%20runs%20a%20sustainable%20mud%20homestay%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanhau.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETanhau%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20runs%20on%2095%20percent%20of%20solar%20energy%20and%20harvested%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20constructing%20his%20home%20and%20the%20homestay%20huts%2C%20Sunando%20considered%20the%20surrounding%20habitat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20nature%20around%20the%20place.%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20add%20to%20the%20carbon%20footprint.%20Instead%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20minimise%20it%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20slow%20and%20sustainable%20tourism%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunando%20wakes%20up%20with%20the%20sun%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331901%2Fcouple-quit-job-to-build-eco-friendly-carbon-negative-home-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreathtaking%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Once%20he%20is%20up%2C%20he%20takes%20his%20five%20dogs%20on%20a%20stroll%20to%20enjoy%20nature%20and%20hopefully%20spot%20some%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20Corbett%20is%20a%20valley%2C%20we%20are%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill.%20So%20we%20get%20a%20striking%20view%20of%20the%20mountains%2C%20and%20we%20also%20get%20a%20lot%2